who I made. It s complicated.

984
00:55:25,000 --> 00:55:26,280
Wait a minute.

985
00:55:26,400 --> 00:55:28,120
You're rejecting me?

986
00:55:28,240 --> 00:55:29,200
I'm sorry.

987
00:55:29,320 --> 00:55:31,880
For that big bumpy thing?

988
00:55:32,960 --> 00:55:33,880
How do you know about...

989
00:55:34,000 --> 00:55:39,400
I mean, this isn't even the sexiest me,
but come on! Look at you.

990
00:55:39,520 --> 00:55:42,640
You're hideous.
You really are.

991
00:55:42,760 --> 00:55:44,760
